short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Move all active tabs from an incognito to a normal window

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
IMPORTANT: "Allow in Incognito" needs to be checked in order for it to work!

A handy Chrome extension that simplifies your browsing experience by allowing you to effortlessly transfer all your active tabs from an incognito window to a normal window with a single click. No more copy-pasting URLs or manually moving tabs one by one. The Un-Incognit-izer ensures a seamless transition, maintaining your workflow and saving time. Perfect for users who often switch between private and regular browsing, this tool enhances productivity and convenience. Install now and streamline your browsing experience!
